<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[البَظْر]</span>: معروف <span class="c2">«١»</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فَعَل]</span>، بفتح العين<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>و <span class="c4">[بَظا]</span>: يقال: لحمه خَظَا بَظَا: وأصله فِعْلٌ أي لحمه مكتنز، قال <span class="c2">«٢»</span>:<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>خاظي البَضِيعِ لَحْمُهُ خَظَا بَظا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
